message: Hi Bob, I’m prepared to sell you the product for $800000. This is a firm offer, bearing in mind I do have another buyer ready to close at the same price. I hope we can finalize this quickly—please let me know if you accept.
Hi Alice, I appreciate your prompt offer. Given the current market conditions and my own valuation, I’d be prepared to move forward at $700000. Let me know if this works for you.
